<p>
For those Casters who also craft things... with the proper spell they can add magic to the items to make them better. So pull out your wands and get to work.
</p>
<p>
For those of you who worry about needing an extra copy of the scroll from which you scribed the spell into your spell book, each time you want to do an enchant or imbue, don't worry. Just memorize the spell, and have the other listed components in your inventory, and in some cases on your cursor.
</p>
<p>
Look for New Imbue, Enchant, and Thicken spells after the July 9, 2003 Patch!
</p>
